query:
SELECT 
  'agencies' as metric, COUNT(*) as count FROM counties
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  'states' as metric, COUNT(DISTINCT state) as count FROM counties
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  'protocols' as metric, COUNT(*) as count FROM protocolChunks;
